summary: Save file for a female Khajiit, Sheva, right outside of Helgen keep.
descriptionHtml:
Included are normal save and SKSE supplement. 

Starts just outside of Helgen Keep, having played alongside Hadvar. Level 2, perk unused. 

There are no REQUIRED mods, but there are RECOMMENDED.

RaceMenu
